\c 30
\s Ubuze bokwenza isivumelwano leGibhithe
\p
\v 1 Maye ebantwaneni abahlamukayo!\x + 30.9. Hlab. 68.6.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuthi benze icebo\x + 29.15.\x*, kodwa elingeyisilo elami, lokuthi bembese ngesembeso\x + 25.7.\x*, kodwa esingesiso \add so\add*moya wami, ukuze bengezelele isono phezu kwesono\x + Dute. 29.19.\x*.
\v 2 Abahamba ukwehlela eGibhithe\x + 31.1.\x*, njalo bengabuzanga umlomo wami\x + Nani 27.21. 1 Kho. 22.7. Jer. 21.2.\x*, ukuze baziqinise emandleni kaFaro, bathembele emthunzini weGibhithe!\x + Nani 14.9.\x*
\v 3 Ngakho amandla kaFaro azakuba lihlazo kini, lokuthembela\x + 36.6,9. 30.7. 20.5. 31.1. Jer. 37.5,7.\x* emthunzini weGibhithe\x + Nani 14.9.\x* kube yikuyangeka.
\v 4 Ngoba iziphathamandla zakhe zaziseZowani\x + Nani 13.22.\x* lezithunywa zakhe\x + Hez. 17.15.\x* zafika eHanesi\x + Jer. 43.7.\x*.
\v 5 Bonke izabayangisa\x + Jer. 2.36.\x* ngabantu ababengelakubasiza\x + 30.6.\x*, bangabi luncedo njalo bangabi yinzuzo, kodwa babe luyangiso njalo babe lihlazo.
