\v 6 Umthwalo\x + 13.1.\x* wezilo zeningizimu\x + 51.9. Jobe 40.15. Hlab. 68.30. Hez. 29.3.\x*. Elizweni lokucindezelwa\x + 8.22.\x* lembandezelo\x + 8.22.\x*, lapho okuvela khona ibhongo lesilwane\x + Jobe 4.11. Zaga 30.30.\x*, ibululu\x + 14.29.\x*\x + Jobe 20.16.\x* lenyoka ephaphayo elokutshisa\x + 14.29.\x*\x + Nani 21.6.\x*, bathwala inotho yabo\x + 57.9. Hos. 12.1.\x* emhlana wamathole abobabhemi\x + 30.24. Hlu. 10.4. 12.14.\x*, lokuligugu kwabo phezu kwamalunda amakamela\x + 57.9. Hos. 12.1.\x*, bekusa ebantwini abangelasizo\x + 30.6.\x*.
\v 7 Ngoba amaGibhithe\x + 30.7. 20.5. 31.1. 36.6,9. Jer. 37.5,7.\x* azasiza ngeze langokungelalutho; ngakho ngakhala ngalokhu \add ngathi\add*: Amandla abo yikuhlala bathule\x + Jobe 9.13.\x*.
