\v 8 Khathesi hamba, ukubhale\x + Hab. 2.2.\x* phambi kwabo esibhebheni, ukulobe ngokugubha egwalweni\x + Jobe 19.23.\x*, ukuze kube khona kuze kube lusuku lokucina, kuze kube nininini, kuze kube phakade.
\v 9 Ngoba bangabantu abavukelayo\x + 1.4. 30.1. Dute. 32.20.\x*, abantwana abaqamba amanga, abantwana abangathandi ukuzwa umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*;
\v 10 abathi kubaboni: Lingaboni\x + 1 Sam. 9.9.\x*; lakubakhangeli: Lingasikhangeleli izinto eziqondileyo\x + Jer. 11.21. Amos 2.12. 7.13. Mika 2.6.\x*; khulumani kithi izinto ezibutshelezi\x + 1 Kho. 22.13.\x*, likhangele izinkohliso;
\v 11 phumani endleleni, liphambuke lisuke emkhondweni, lisuse oNgcwele kaIsrayeli phambi kwethu.
\v 12 Ngakho utsho njalo oNgcwele kaIsrayeli \add uthi\add*: Ngoba lidelele lelilizwi, lathembela kucindezelo lokuphambeneyo\x + 1 Kho. 22.13.\x*, labambelela kukho.
\v 13 Ngakho lobububi buzakuba kini njengomkenke osuzakuwa, ukhukhumala emdulini omude, okudilika kwawo kuhle kufike\x + Zaga 6.15.\x* masinyazana\x + Zaga 6.15.\x*\x + 29.5.\x*.
\v 14 Yebo, uzawephula\x + Hlab. 2.9.\x* njengokwephulwa kwembiza yababumbi ephahaziweyo; kayikuyekela\x + Hlab. 2.9.\x*, ukuze kungatholakali ezicucwini zayo udengezi\x + Hez. 23.24.\x* lokokha umlilo eziko\x + Hez. 47.11.\x*, kumbe ukukha amanzi emthonjeni\x + Hez. 47.11.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova, oNgcwele kaIsrayeli: Ngokuphenduka lokuphumula lizasindiswa\x + 28.12. Jobe 36.16.\x*; ngokuthula\x + 7.4. Eks. 14.14.\x* langokwethemba kuzakuba ngamandla enu; kodwa kalifunanga\x + Mat. 23.37.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa lathi: Hatshi, ngoba sizabaleka ngamabhiza\x + 31.1. Hos. 14.3.\x*; ngakho-ke lizabaleka; njalo: Sizagada\x + 31.1. Hos. 14.3.\x* \add amabhiza\add* alejubane\x + 18.2.\x*; ngakho-ke abalixotshayo bazakuba lejubane.
\v 17 Inkulungwane eyodwa\x + Levi 26.8. Dute. 28.25.\x* \add izabaleka\add* ngokukhalima koyedwa; ngokukhalima kwabahlanu lizabaleka, lize lisale njengensika phezu kwengqonga yentaba, lanjengesiboniso\x + 33.23.\x* phezu koqaqa.
\s Isithembiso sikaNkulunkulu ebantwini bakhe
\p
\v 18 Ngakho-ke iN\nd kosi\nd* izalinda\x + Roma 2.4.\x*, ukuze ibe lomusa kini, ngakho-ke izaphakanyiswa\x + Hlab. 46.10.\x* ukuthi ibe lesihawu kini; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* \add ing\add*uNkulunkulu wesahlulelo; babusisiwe bonke abalindela kuyo\x + Hlab. 2.12. 33.20.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Ngoba abantu bazahlala eZiyoni eJerusalema\x + 65.9,19.\x*; kaliyikukhala lokukhala inyembezi; izakuba lomusa omkhulu kuwe elizwini lokukhala kwakho; lapho ilizwa izakuphendula.
\v 20 Loba iNkosi ilinika isinkwa sosizi\x + 1 Kho. 22.27. Hlab. 127.2.\x* lamanzi okuhlupheka\x + 1 Kho. 22.27.\x*, kanti abafundisi bakho kabasayikususelwa engonsini\x + Hlab. 74.9.\x*, kodwa amehlo akho azabona abafundisi bakho.
\v 21 Lendlebe zakho zizakuzwa ilizwi emva kwakho lisithi: Le yiyo indlela, hambani ngayo\x + 35.8. Seb. 9.2.\x*, lapho liphambukela ngakwesokunene lalapho liphambukela ngakwesokhohlo\x + Dute. 5.32.\x*.
\v 22 Lizangcolisa lokuhuqiweyo\x + Nani 16.38,39.\x* kwezithombe zakho ezibaziweyo\x + 2.20. 31.7.\x* zesiliva, lokunanyekiweyo kwezithombe zakho zegolide ezibunjwe ngokuncibilikisa\x + Eks. 28.8. 39.5.\x*; lizihlakaze njengelembu losesikhathini\x + Esta 1.6. 1 Kor. 4.13.\x*, lithi kuzo: Phumani!\x + Hos. 14.8.\x*
\v 23 Khona izanika izulu lenhlanyelo yakho ozayihlanyela emhlabathini, lesinkwa sesivuno somhlaba; uzavunda ucicime. Ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x* izifuyo zenu zizakudla emadlelweni abanzi\x + Hlab. 65.13.\x*;
\v 24 lezinkabi\x + 32.20.\x* labobabhemi abatsha\x + 30.6.\x* okulima umhlabathi\x + Gen. 45.6.\x* kuzakudla umncantsha\x + Jobe 24.6.\x*, oweliweyo ngefotsholo langefologwe.
\v 25 Laphezu kwayo yonke intaba ende\x + 2.14,15.\x* laphezu kwalo lonke uqaqa oluphakemeyo\x + 2.14,15.\x* kuzakuba lemifula \add le\add*zifudlana zamanzi\x + 44.4.\x* ngosuku lokubulawa okukhulu, lapho kusiwa imiphotshongo\x + 2.14,15.\x*.
\v 26 Futhi ukukhanya\x + 60.19,20.\x* kwenyanga kuzakuba njengokukhanya kwelanga, lokukhanya kwelanga kuphindwe kasikhombisa\x + Hlab. 79.12.\x*, njengokukhanya kwensuku eziyisikhombisa, mhla iN\nd kosi\nd* ibopha ukwephuka kwabantu bayo, ipholisa\x + Jobe 5.18.\x* umvimvinya wesilonda sabo.
\s Ukunqotshwa kweAsiriya
\p
\v 27 Khangela, ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* livela khatshana, livutha ulaka lwayo, lomthwalo unzima; indebe zayo zigcwele intukuthelo, lolimi lwayo lunjengomlilo oqothulayo;
\v 28 lokuphefumula kwayo\x + 11.4. 2 Thes. 2.8.\x* kunjengesifula esiphuphumayo size sifike phakathi kwentamo\x + 8.8.\x*, ukuhlungula izizwe ngesihlungulo sobuze\x + 27.8.\x*; njalo kuzakuba letomu\x + 37.29.\x* eliduhisayo emihlathini yabantu.
\v 29 Lizakuba lengoma, njengeyobusuku bokwehlukaniswa komkhosi, lokuthokoza kwenhliziyo, njengohamba lomhubhe\x + 1 Kho. 1.40.\x* esiya entabeni yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 2.3.\x*, eDwaleni lakoIsrayeli.
\v 30 IN\nd kosi\nd* izazwakalisa-ke ilizwi layo elilodumo, ibonakalise ukwehla kwengalo yayo\x + Jobe 36.16. Hlab. 125.3.\x*, ngentukuthelo yolaka, lelangabi lomlilo oqothulayo\x + 29.6.\x*, isivunguvungu, lezulu lesiphepho\x + 28.2.\x*, lesiqhotho\x + 28.2.\x*\x + Josh. 10.11.\x*.
\v 31 Ngoba ngelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 37.36.\x* amaAsiriya azaphahlazwa\x + 31.4.\x*, itshaya ngenduku\x + 10.5,24.\x*.
\v 32 Kuzakuthi loba ngaphi okwedlula khona induku emisiweyo, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyibeka phezu kwayo, kube ngezigubhu\x + 5.12.\x* langamachacho\x + 5.12.\x*, langezimpi zokunyikinya\x + 11.15. 19.16. 2.19.\x* ilwe labo.
\v 33 Ngoba iThofethi\x + 26.14. 2 Kho. 23.10.\x* yahlelwa endulo, layo yamiselwa inkosi\x + 16.5. Mat. 25.41.\x*; yayenza yatshona, yaba banzi, inqumbi yayo ingumlilo lenkuni ezinengi\x + Hez. 24.9.\x*; ukuphefumula kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuyayithungela\x + Hez. 20.48.\x* njengesifula \w sesolufa\w**.